{"image_id": "KEY_2015_page_195", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "KeyBank’s long-term senior unsecured credit rating was four ratings above noninvestment grade at Moody’s and", "bbox": [162.5, 159.1, 1107.2, 179.9]}, {"text": "S&P as of December 31, 2015, and December 31, 2014. If KeyBank’s ratings had been downgraded below", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 1055.4, 204.9]}, {"text": "investment grade as of December 31, 2015, and December 31, 2014, payments of up to $5 million would have", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1083.6, 229.9]}, {"text": "been required to either terminate the contracts or post additional collateral for those contracts in a net liability", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 1077.0, 254.9]}, {"text": "position, taking into account all collateral already posted. If KeyCorp’s ratings had been downgraded below", "bbox": [162.5, 259.1, 1063.1, 279.9]}, {"text": "investment grade as of December 31, 2015, and December 31, 2014, payments of less than $1 million would", "bbox": [162.5, 284.1, 1069.3, 304.9]}, {"text": "have been required to either terminate the contracts or post additional collateral for those contracts in a net", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 1051.5, 329.9]}, {"text": "liability position, taking into account all collateral already posted.", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 711.2, 354.9]}, {"text": "9. Mortgage Servicing Assets", "bbox": [483.2, 402.6, 791.8, 427.6]}, {"text": "We originate and periodically sell commercial mortgage loans but continue to service those loans for the buyers.", "bbox": [162.5, 452.4, 1102.3, 473.2]}, {"text": "We also may purchase the right to service commercial mortgage loans for other lenders. We record a servicing", "bbox": [162.5, 477.4, 1086.5, 498.2]}, {"text": "asset if we purchase or retain the right to service loans in exchange for servicing fees that exceed the going", "bbox": [162.5, 502.4, 1054.6, 523.2]}, {"text": "market servicing rate and are considered more than adequate compensation for servicing. Changes in the carrying", "bbox": [162.5, 527.4, 1110.7, 548.2]}, {"text": "amount of mortgage servicing assets are summarized as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 552.4, 701.6, 573.2]}, {"text": "Year ended December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 597.6, 345.8, 614.3]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [162.5, 618.4, 233.3, 635.1]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [966.7, 618.4, 1000.0, 635.1]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1079.2, 618.4, 1112.5, 635.1]}, {"text": "Balance at beginning of period", "bbox": [162.5, 645.7, 367.8, 662.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [908.3, 645.5, 916.7, 662.2]}, {"text": "323", "bbox": [975.0, 645.5, 1000.0, 662.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1020.8, 645.7, 1029.2, 662.4]}, {"text": "332", "bbox": [1087.5, 645.7, 1112.5, 662.4]}, {"text": "Servicing retained from loan sales", "bbox": [162.5, 666.5, 389.8, 683.2]}, {"text": "55", "bbox": [983.3, 666.4, 1000.0, 683.0]}, {"text": "38", "bbox": [1095.8, 666.5, 1112.5, 683.2]}, {"text": "Purchases", "bbox": [162.5, 687.4, 229.2, 704.0]}, {"text": "38", "bbox": [983.3, 687.2, 1000.0, 703.9]}, {"text": "51", "bbox": [1095.8, 687.4, 1112.5, 704.0]}, {"text": "Amortization", "bbox": [162.5, 708.2, 251.4, 724.9]}, {"text": "(94)", "bbox": [977.8, 708.0, 1005.6, 724.7]}, {"text": "(98)", "bbox": [1090.3, 708.2, 1118.0, 724.9]}, {"text": "Balance at end of period", "bbox": [162.5, 735.3, 325.3, 751.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [908.3, 735.1, 916.7, 751.8]}, {"text": "322", "bbox": [975.0, 735.1, 1000.0, 751.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1020.8, 735.3, 1029.2, 751.9]}, {"text": "323", "bbox": [1087.5, 735.3, 1112.5, 751.9]}, {"text": "Fair value at end of period", "bbox": [162.5, 774.9, 338.6, 791.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [908.3, 774.7, 916.7, 791.4]}, {"text": "423", "bbox": [975.0, 774.7, 1000.0, 791.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1020.8, 774.9, 1029.2, 791.5]}, {"text": "417", "bbox": [1087.5, 774.9, 1112.5, 791.5]}, {"text": "The fair value of mortgage servicing assets is determined by calculating the present value of future cash flows", "bbox": [162.5, 83